<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Happy Birthday, My Lifeline</title>
 
<style>
    body {
        margin: 0;
        background: pink;
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
        text-align: center;
        overflow-x: hidden;
    }
 
    h1 {
        color: #d4006e;
        font-size: 3rem;
        margin-top: 30px;
        animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in-out;
    }
 
    p {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        color: #b30059;
        padding: 0 20px;
        animation: fadeIn 3s ease-in-out;
    }
 
    .gallery {
        margin-top: 30px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 20px;
    }
 
    .gallery img {
        width: 80%;
        max-width: 400px;
        border-radius: 15px;
        border: 4px solid #ffaad6;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(255,0,106,0.5);
        animation: zoomIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
    }
 
    .heart-anim {
        font-size: 40px;
        animation: float 3s infinite ease-in-out;
        color: #ff006a;
    }
 
    @keyframes float {
        0% { transform: translateY(0);}
        50% { transform: translateY(-15px);}
        100% { transform: translateY(0);}
    }
 
    @keyframes fadeIn {
        from { opacity: 0;}
        to { opacity: 1;}
    }
 
    @keyframes zoomIn {
        from { transform: scale(0.5); opacity: 0;}
        to { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1;}
    }
 
    .music {
        margin-top: 20px;
    }
 
    .animated-gif {
        width: 200px;
        margin-top: 20px;
    }
</style>
</head>
 
<body>
 
<h1>Happy Birthday to My Love, My Lifeline</h1>
 
<p>
    Thank you for being the light of my world, the strength in every storm,  
    and the person whose love feels like home.  
    Today is your day — and you deserve all the joy, peace, and happiness life can give.
</p>
 
<div class="heart-anim">💖💗💞</div>
 
<div class="animated-gif">
    <img src="[i.gifer.com](https://i.gifer.com/7efs.gif)" width="200">
</div>
 
<div class="music">
    <audio controls autoplay>
        <source src="[files.freemusicarchive.org](https://files.freemusicarchive.org/storage-freemusicarchive-org/music/no_curator/Loyalty_Freak_Music/LO-FI_SAX/LO-FI_SAX_-_01_-_Lofi_Sax.mp3)">
    </audio>
 
    <audio controls>
        <source src="[files.freemusicarchive.org](https://files.freemusicarchive.org/storage-freemusicarchive-org/music/no_curator/Komiku/Its_time_for_adventure/Komiku_-_03_-_Friends_And_Flowers.mp3)">
    </audio>
</div>
 
<h2 style="color:#d4006e; margin-top:40px;">Our Beautiful Moments</h2>
 
<div class="gallery">
 
    <img src="img1.jpg" alt="Photo 1">
    <img src="img2.jpg" alt="Photo 2">
    <img src="img3.jpg" alt="Photo 3">
    <img src="img4.jpg" alt="Photo 4">
    <img src="img5.jpg" alt="Photo 5">
    <img src="img6.jpg" alt="Photo 6">
    <img src="img7.jpg" alt="Photo 7">
 
</div>
 
<p style="margin-top:40px; font-weight: bold;">
    You are cherished beyond words.  
    Always and forever.
</p>
 
<div class="heart-anim">💗✨💗</div>
 
</body>
</html>
